OL,3,CDumfries charity cafe to cut staff by
OL,4,C50% amid soaring costs
OL,6,FThe Usual Place in Dumfries has been
OL,7,Foperating since 2015, and comprises a
OL,8,Flarge cafe and adjoining meeting space
OL,9,Fin the former Townhead Church
OL,10,Fbuilding. It describes itself as a
OL,11,F"skills academy," providing young
OL,12,Fpeople with additional needs training
OL,13,Fand mentorship aimed at giving them
OL,14,Fthe skills needed to join the
OL,15,Fworkforce.
