OL,3,CDumfries charity cafe to cut staff by
OL,4,C50% amid soaring costs
OL,6,FBut now the charity have blamed a
OL,7,Flooming rise in employer national
OL,8,Finsurance contributions as well as an
OL,9,Fuplift in the real living wage for
OL,10,Fleaving them in an "unsustainable
OL,11,Fsituation."
OL,13,FThe increase in costs has created a
OL,14,F"perfect storm," ITV News Border was
OL,15,Ftold, with a staffing bill of more
OL,16,Fthan #700,000 for 2025-26. The charity
OL,17,Fsay they've secured funding of just
OL,18,Funder #500,000.
