OL,3,CDumfries charity cafe to cut staff by
OL,4,C50% amid soaring costs
OL,6,FIn a statement announcing the cuts The
OL,7,FUsual Place described itself as "more
OL,8,Fthan a cafe."
OL,10,F"We are a unique skills academy where
OL,11,Fpotential is nurtured, confidence is
OL,12,Fbuilt, futures are shaped, and an
OL,13,Finclusive workforce is created," the
OL,14,Fstatement read.
OL,16,F"We face an undeniable financial
OL,17,Freality: we will never be able to make
OL,18,Fenough cups of tea to cover all our
OL,19,Fcosts.
