OL,3,CDumfries charity cafe to cut staff by
OL,4,C50% amid soaring costs
OL,6,F"Rising costs, including a projected
OL,7,F#25K increase in National Insurance
OL,8,Fand #26K in Real Living Wage costs
OL,9,Ffrom April, alongside inflation in the
OL,10,Fcosts of produce and utilities, are
OL,11,Fcreating financial pressures we cannot
OL,12,Fignore."
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV News Border Craig
OL,15,FMcEwen, the CEO of the organisation
OL,16,Fwhich runs the Usual Place, described
OL,17,Fthe incoming cuts as "heartbreaking."
