OL,3,CDumfries charity cafe to cut staff by
OL,4,C50% amid soaring costs
OL,6,F"We were set up to fill a gap that our
OL,7,Fyoung people needed, to get those live
OL,8,Fskills to make them constructive
OL,9,Fcitizens in society, instead of just
OL,10,Frecipients of passive care " he said.
OL,12,FThe charity say restructuring will see
OL,13,Fthe equivalent of six full time roles
OL,14,Flost, which could affect up to half
OL,15,Fthe workforce. Employees with
OL,16,Fadditional needs could be among those
OL,17,Faffected, as are mentoring positions,
OL,18,Fwhich the charity described as "roles
OL,19,Fat the heart of our work."
