OL,3,CDumfries charity cafe to cut staff by
OL,4,C50% amid soaring costs
OL,6,FIn October the Chancellor Rachel
OL,7,FReeves announced, among other
OL,8,Fmeasures, an increase in employers
OL,9,Fnational insurance in order to better
OL,10,Ffund public services.
OL,12,FIn a statement a Treasury Spokesperson
OL,13,Fsaid: "We support our charities
OL,14,Fthrough a world-leading tax regime
OL,15,Fwhich provided #6bn in relief for the
OL,16,Fsector last year alone, including
OL,17,Fexemptions from paying business rates.
